{"type": "article", "id": 35525, "title": "AA获3000万破产贷款，以及，emoji家族新增了近百个新表情 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-13T02:37:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 791, "name": "Emoji"}, {"id": 2488, "name": "J.Crew"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 16038, "name": "BAPE"}, {"id": 35744, "name": "mastermind JAPAN"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161213094345TZwYbuf68eBD1Slc.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/american-apparel-wins-approval-of-its-bankruptcy-loan-1481573015\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>American Apparel 获得 3000 万美元破产贷款</b></a> | 周一，美国威尔明顿法院通过了 American Apparel 的破产贷款。到目前为止，AA 的分销业务已经得到了加拿大 GILDAN 运动服公司的 6600 万美元的出价，不过，它的商店和库存资产仍然在寻找买主。这部分业务或将于 1 月 6 日提交报价，将于 1 月 9 日进行公开拍卖。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.retaildive.com/news/j-crew-reportedly-in-talks-to-restructure-2b-debt/432154/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>J.Crew 正在洽谈债务重组</b></a> | 据路透社消息称，J.Crew 正在与它的债权人洽谈，将进行 20 亿美元的债务重组。J.Crew 的现金短缺致使它最近放弃了它的新娘业务，在九月公布的第二季度总收入下降了 4%，至 5.698 亿美元，同店销售额同比下降了 8%。路透社在上个月也曾报道，为了保护债权人的利益，根据 J.Crew 的债务状况，或将出售 Madewell 品牌。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/visvim-pins-badges-treasures\" rel=\"nofollow\">visvim 推出两组美式风格的胸针系列</a>，其中，Treasures 系列共六枚，包括美国国旗、图腾、印第安人头像等形状。Badges 系列共四枚，皆是圆形徽章。目前这两组胸针已经在 visvim 的线上商店出售，售价分别为 300 和 115 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612131012254CDtJpT5X9yFcozH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101235NdK5pSvWMkltyYUa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/size-x-vans-old-skool-wool-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 与英国球鞋店铺 size？合作发布 Old Skool 系列</a>，该系列的灵感来自剪裁精良的羊毛大衣，选用了黑、红、灰三种羊毛材质，目前已于 size？独家发售，定价为 60 英镑。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101147109YDlQJG3SnNTbq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101147IzvGjUyQl08cxwWg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101158Yw6cN7OUeKyusHDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101158TlDEMB7y8jRbiQPk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101159qfamyvLQZ6rsDcS1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/bottega-veneta-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bottega Veneta 发布 2017 年早秋系列 lookbook</a>，以品牌独有的 Intercciato 的皮革编织为标志，并加入了几何图样搭配。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101259qZXWub9m4aohjcUB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101300JhPiXASOR2wNo8sL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101300GVf3ytjws2CgOIq9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101300OEsZmYFqiwDfBvc1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016121310130918asufQKgyIHvXZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101309FXkzCw35nMytI2QD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101309DJFkeglQhGqsWRux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101309AqofPlctQ8uwik0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612131013099guOU2s1q8WfEjtP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101309fVTl84CpQs37hWBP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.913265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>昨日，<a href=\"http://www.apple.com/newsroom/2016/12/apple-adds-hundreds-of-new-and-redesigned-emoji-in-ios-102.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">苹果 iOS10.2.2 里又增添了上百个新的 emoji 表情</a>, 包括说假话的“长鼻子”、“Finger Cross”、“牛油果”、“牛角面包”、“呕吐”、“流口水”等。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101125sn5Ov1Hk2VKeSZ4a.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.992883\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101125z8PCB0teQOXwvN5A.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.996198\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016121310112535Fo0UPx2wqJC9MK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.950877\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101134youakHFROW9l4NAi.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.980000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612131011342gln1dtjmARfPBu7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.024809\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/10/carrots-neon-champion-sweatsuits-winter-2016/#slide-11\" rel=\"nofollow\">洛杉矶街头品牌 Carrots 与 Champion 合作</a>，发布了一个连帽衫和运动裤系列。该系列共有藏青、浅灰、黑色三种颜色，已于 Carrots 官网发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101322ODaMQ6dSqmTs8nlX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101322DtVBrC37pbE4vJ8K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101350iqdpGOcArPZCnsTu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/bape-x-mastermind-japan-collection-and-pricing\" rel=\"nofollow\">《SENSE》杂志曝光了 BAPE 和 mastermind JAPAN 的联名系列造型特辑和价格信息</a>。在外套方面，有 Rain Jacket，还有今年流行的  Souvenir Jacket 和 MA-1 Jacket，此外还包括连帽衫、圆领卫衣、运动裤、皮制棒球帽及针织冷帽。其中，最便宜的 T-shirt 售价为 9000 日元，最贵的单品是 60000 日元的 Rain Jacket。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101404FbpahHle9kYIWJB2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101404279lOvcBq518wLfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161213101404XUs4fT7BheQ5qAVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}